{"tid":2068124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求中央政府收回海參崴，以保領土完整","createTime":"2020-06-17T12:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T05:22:44.000Z","uid":359711,"like":122,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ce6bb229d147e8bd9a8663aa0b22c011d11030d7","tid":2068124,"uid":359711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:20:32.000Z","msg":"海參崴自新石器時代時起便有人類居住，原為遊牧民族居住地，後歷為渤海國、遼朝、金朝、元朝、明朝、清朝領土，1860年清朝與俄羅斯帝國簽訂《中俄北京條約》，將此地永久割讓予俄羅斯，改由俄羅斯帝國統治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n永久割讓只是清朝的承諾，咱們已經從英國鬼手上把香港拿回來了，習大大請帶領中國人民，從俄羅斯人手上把海參崴拿回來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b3166b843141a0e874236035c6847bfa6a7bb5","tid":2068124,"uid":300782,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534dab4b4b885403839ce1f86043469f0cb2ee63","tid":2068124,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"大興安嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82708a3c7a9917a8b9c9b3c0a894445c8f066725","tid":2068124,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"外興安嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37301e28d520e4475e4332fc79a990d9cb0c0bd5","tid":2068124,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"不平等條約"},{"pid":"c209af08bd5e4af928e9841572b6c5001a899f74","tid":2068124,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"越南<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72859241a14978fe4fc3699425a49fa92959f363","tid":2068124,"uid":359711,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"自從習大大上任以來，把新彊跟香港鎮壓得妥妥當當，我們是時候向俄國人拿回海參崴，振興我大中華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},